subject: Article That Should Help Testing: "Five Habits of Highly Profitable Software Dev
msgSnippet: Hello, Today, I have a test related article being published on java.net: Five Habits of Highly Profitable Software Developers
messageBody:
Hello,

Today, I have a test related article being published on java.net:
"Five Habits of Highly Profitable Software Developers"
http://today.java.net/pub/a/today/2006/08/24/five-habits-of-highly-profitable-developers.html

If you have a moment, please give it a read and let me know what you
think. If you like it, please encourage your colleagues to read it too.

Thank you,
Rob Miller

p.s. I apologize for not using JUnit 5 in my examples.
